room_title: Escape room "Alpha-Omega Virus" by The Door Escape Room in Charlotte
room_address: 204 W Woodlawn Rd. Suite D1 Charlotte, NC 28217
room_description:
Evil Dr. Jacob Jacoby has synthesized one of the deadliest viruses known to man - The Alpha-Omega Virus. As any "good" scientist, he has created the anti-virus as well to cure anyone infected. The bad news is he has hidden clues to synthesizing it somewhere in his high-security lab. The good news is, if found and created in time, you will be saving all of mankind.
Can you sneak into his lab to find the ingredients to create the cure and escape before his return? Humanity's fate is in your team's hands - NO PRESSURE!
